<section class="solution" id="solution">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">The Caliro Approach</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle">
      A complete reimagining of the Android experience, built for intentional use
    </p>
    
    <div class="approach-grid">
      <div class="approach-item">
        <div class="approach-number">01</div>
        <h3>Mindful by Default</h3>
        <p>No addictive patterns, no dark UX. Every interaction is designed to respect your attention and time.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="approach-item">
        <div class="approach-number">02</div>
        <h3>Friction Where It Matters</h3>
        <p>Smart barriers that make you pause before engaging with potentially problematic content or apps.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="approach-item">
        <div class="approach-number">03</div>
        <h3>Insight & Awareness</h3>
        <p>Understand your usage patterns with compassionate, non-judgmental tracking and insights.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="approach-item">
        <div class="approach-number">04</div>
        <h3>Community-Driven</h3>
        <p>Open source and transparent. Built with input from people who understand the struggle firsthand.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="philosophy">
      <h3>Our Philosophy</h3>
      <p>
        Technology should serve you, not exploit you. Caliro isn't about restriction - 
        it's about creating an environment where mindful choices are the easy choices. 
        Where your phone becomes a tool again, not a trap.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .solution {
    padding: 100px 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc 0%, #e0e7ff 100%);
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-weight: 800;
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--color-gray);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
  }

  .approach-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .approach-item {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .approach-number {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    line-height: 60px;
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 50%;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .approach-item h3 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-dark);
  }

  .approach-item p {
    color: var(--color-gray);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .philosophy {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
    background: white;
    padding: 3rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
  }

  .philosophy h3 {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-dark);
  }

  .philosophy p {
    color: var(--color-gray);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
</style>